      • onARDrone3PilotingStateSpeedChangedUpdate

        void onARDrone3PilotingStateSpeedChangedUpdate(float speedX,
                                             float speedY,
                                             float speedZ)
        Called when a command SpeedChanged of class PilotingState in project ARDrone3 is decoded
        Parameters:
        _speedX - Speed on the x axis (when drone moves forward, speed is > 0) (in m/s)
        _speedY - Speed on the y axis (when drone moves to right, speed is > 0) (in m/s)
        _speedZ - Speed on the z axis (when drone moves down, speed is > 0) (in m/s)
